# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:12
translate chinese whitneyq4_e73edfc6:

    # wt "Are you afraid of going through the hoop?"
    wt "你怕走这套程序吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:16
translate chinese whitneyq4_de003d77:

    # pc "I'm just ready to do it."
    pc "我只是准备好了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:17
translate chinese whitneyq4_234123d7:

    # pc "I trust that you know what you're doing."
    pc "我相信你知道自己在做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:18
translate chinese whitneyq4_1968b38a:

    # pc "I trust you to take care of everything, when it's time."
    pc "我相信到时候你会处理好一切。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:20
translate chinese whitneyq4_82298393:

    # wt "It will be time soon, I think. I am almost ready."
    wt "我想很快就会到那一步了。我几乎已经准备好了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:22
translate chinese whitneyq4_1a57731c:

    # wt "I might be more nervous about it than you are."
    wt "我可能比你还要紧张。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:25
translate chinese whitneyq4_808f0c76:

    # pc "I'm a little worried."
    pc "我有点担心。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:26
translate chinese whitneyq4_4364da66:

    # pc "I know that you know what you are doing, but it's still scary."
    pc "我知道你心里有数，但这还是让人害怕。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:27
translate chinese whitneyq4_3854f192:

    # pc "That's not going to stop me from doing it though."
    pc "不过这不会阻止我这么做。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:29
translate chinese whitneyq4_340495cb:

    # wt "I am a little worried, as well."
    wt "我也有点担心。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:30
translate chinese whitneyq4_2a4d084d:

    # wt "I'm confident in my abilities, but there is a lot on the line."
    wt "我对自己的能力很有信心，但这次赌注太大了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:33
translate chinese whitneyq4_f0f44364:

    # pc "I know that you know what you're doing, but if something goes wrong, I could be stuck wherever my dad is."
    pc "我知道你很清楚自己在做什么，但如果出了差错，我可能会被困在爸爸所在的地方。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:34
translate chinese whitneyq4_db92c80f:

    # pc "Or worse."
    pc "或者更糟。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:35
translate chinese whitneyq4_c379f716:

    # pc "I love my life here. I don't want to lose that."
    pc "我喜欢这里的生活。我不想失去这一切。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:37
translate chinese whitneyq4_264386a1:

    # wt "I understand."
    wt "我理解。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:38
translate chinese whitneyq4_fce90c44:

    # wt "I am very confident in my abilities, but there are many things that could go wrong."
    wt "我对自己的能力非常有信心，但可能出错的地方太多了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:39
translate chinese whitneyq4_3bfad435:

    # wt "Even though I can minimize those risks, I cannot eliminate them."
    wt "虽然我能把风险降到最低，却无法完全消除。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:41
translate chinese whitneyq4_289a8839:

    # wt "There is a lot on the line."
    wt "这关系重大。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:42
translate chinese whitneyq4_655dcd08:

    # wt "If you go through and are not able to return, I feel like the police are going to come after me."
    wt "如果你去了却无法回来，我觉得警察会来找我。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:44
translate chinese whitneyq4_0ceee22c:

    # wt "Then if they somehow connect me with the jewelry stores, my work could be in danger."
    wt "如果他们 somehow 把我跟珠宝店联系起来，我的工作可能会有危险。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:46
translate chinese whitneyq4_d2536b63:

    # wt "That really worries me. My work is very important."
    wt "这真的让我很担心。我的工作非常重要。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:48
translate chinese whitneyq4_ff732e57:

    # wt "Also, I wouldn't want you to be trapped wherever your father is, of course."
    wt "当然，我也不希望你被困在你父亲所在的地方。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:49
translate chinese whitneyq4_f4d9a84f:

    # pc "This does not make me any less nervous."
    pc "但这并不能让我少一点紧张。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:51
translate chinese whitneyq4_3d91f7b3:

    # wt "I'm sorry, that was not my intention."
    wt "对不起，我不是那个意思。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq4.rpy:52
translate chinese whitneyq4_2acedf3a:

    # pc "No matter what I feel, I'm going to do it. I want to find my dad."
    pc "无论我心里怎么想，我都要这么做。我想找到我爸爸。"

